---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import larryLogo from "../../assets/larrysmshub_logo.png";
---

<Layout title="Larry SMS Hub">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-8">
    <Header />
    <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-2">
      <a href="/projects" class="underline decoration-dashed underline-offset-4">← Back to projects</a>
    </div>
    <div class="mb-3">
      <img src={larryLogo.src} alt="Larry SMS Hub logo" class="h-10 md:h-12 object-contain" />
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Larry SMS Hub</h1>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-[11px] mb-2">
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-sky-200 text-sky-700 bg-sky-50/60">Beta</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Sender ID</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Bulk SMS</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Delivery reports</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Voice SMS</span>
    </div>
    <p class="text-gray-700 md:w-3/4" style="line-height: 2">
      Branded bulk SMS for businesses — send messages under your business name, simply and reliably.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">
      Built for Ghanaian businesses. NCA‑friendly and focused on dependable delivery.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">What you get</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc ms-5 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>Sender IDs (messages appear from your business name)</li>
          <li>Bulk campaigns and CSV uploads</li>
          <li>Contact groups and simple segmentation</li>
          <li>Scheduling and delivery reports</li>
          <li>Voice SMS (text‑to‑speech calls) for important alerts</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Use cases</h3>
         <ul class="list-disc ms-5 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>Promotions and announcements</li>
          <li>Reminders and notifications</li>
          <li>Community and event outreach</li>
           <li>Voice call alerts (e.g., fee deadlines, appointment follow‑ups)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">How it works</h3>
        <ol class="list-decimal ms-5 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
          <li>Request a Sender ID (your business name) and get approved.</li>
          <li>Upload contacts or CSV, group customers, and compose your message.</li>
          <li>Schedule or send immediately — track delivery in reports.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Stack</h3>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-[11px]">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">MongoDB</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">React Native</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Node.js</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">What people say</h3>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div>
            <blockquote class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              “We set up our Sender ID on Monday and went live by Wednesday. Reminders now go out on time, and I finally trust the delivery reports. It feels… easy.”
            </blockquote>
            <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-500">
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-600">David Walker Amoah</span>
              <span class="opacity-50"> • </span>
              <span>Owner, DWA Services (Accra)</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <blockquote class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              “The branded name alone boosted replies. Scheduling campaigns means I don’t forget anymore.”
            </blockquote>
            <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-500">— Retail manager</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Before / After</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 bg-white/70 p-3">
            <div class="font-semibold">Before</div>
            <ul class="list-disc ms-5 mt-1 text-gray-700 space-y-1">
              <li>Unbranded numbers, low trust</li>
              <li>Manual sends, missed reminders</li>
              <li>No clear delivery insight</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 bg-white/70 p-3">
            <div class="font-semibold">After</div>
            <ul class="list-disc ms-5 mt-1 text-gray-700 space-y-1">
              <li>Sender ID (brand name) on every SMS</li>
              <li>Scheduled campaigns and groups</li>
              <li>Delivery reports you can export</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Pricing</h3>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-700">Pay‑as‑you‑go</div>
        <ul class="list-disc ms-5 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>Only pay for messages sent</li>
          <li>Volume discounts available</li>
          <li>No setup fee for standard Sender IDs</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-2 text-xs text-gray-500">Need enterprise billing or a custom rate? <a class="underline" href="/contact">Contact me</a>.</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">FAQ</h3>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">How long does Sender ID approval take?</div>
            <p class="mt-1">Typically 1–3 business days depending on the provider and name requested.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Can I import my existing contacts?</div>
            <p class="mt-1">Yes. Upload a CSV or paste contacts directly. We’ll help you clean and group them.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Do you support delivery reports?</div>
            <p class="mt-1">Absolutely. Track success and failures with simple, exportable reports.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      <a
        href="mailto:larryhubservices@gmail.com?subject=Larry%20SMS%20Hub%20mobile%20app%20%E2%80%94%20Demo%20request&body=Hi%20Larry%20SMS%20Hub%20team%2C%0D%0A%0D%0AI%E2%80%99d%20like%20a%20demo%20of%20the%20Larry%20SMS%20Hub%20mobile%20application.%0D%0A%0D%0ABusiness%20name%3A%20%0D%0AUse%20case%3A%20(reminders%2C%20promotions%2C%20etc.)%0D%0AEstimated%20monthly%20volume%3A%20%0D%0APreferred%20Sender%20ID%3A%20%0D%0A%0D%0AThanks!"
        class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white/80"
      >Request demo</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

